 737:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/core/lv_obj_pos.c **** 
 738:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/core/lv_obj_pos.c ****         /*If the object is already out of the parent and its position is changes
